Package dev.negativekb.api.util.data

Class BiMap<K,V,V1>

java.lang.Object
dev.negativekb.api.util.data.BiMap<K,V,V1>
Type Parameters:
K - Key (Object)
V - Value 1 (any Type)
V1 - Value 2 (any Type)
public class BiMap<K,V,V1> extends Object
BiMap is an extended version of Map, HashMap, or whatever. This data class can hold 2 values rather than 1 value similar to Map or HashMap and any other data sets that do not hold 2 values.
Since:
August 4th, 2021
Author:
Negative
